audit-password - Password Audit

USAGE:
    audit-password [user1] [user2] ...

DESCRIPTION:
    Audit passwords for users. If no users specified, audits the
    current user. Requires root privileges.

ARGUMENTS:
    user1, user2, ...
        Users to audit (optional, defaults to current user)

EXAMPLES:
    audit-password
    audit-password root
    audit-password user1 user2
